n據悉，死者姓梁(35歲)，家中有父母及姊妹，獨自前來，家人知悉後前往醫院了解，得知親人過世，家人傷心不已。據悉事主留下兩封遺書，其中一封講述家人如何為他辦理身後事，另一封遺書內容主要涉及不滿政府的修訂《逃犯條例》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=103723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Ffi%3Dnews1%26id%3D103723&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=5347f8d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=103723</a>"},{"pid":"7a88bdf5d3e7e4efb0cb10431f635c9e036cbfc2","tid":1229101,"uid":28163,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:38:46.000Z","msg":"遺書唔知<br />\n遺志佢寫得好清楚"},{"pid":"26ab0d5a1dc8000a73581e53b7fa78cf95a319ba","tid":1229101,"uid":56063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"43e02482c968b67b033cbbab143c8304f80e4051","tid":1229101,"uid":228464,"like":147,"dislike":2,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T21:27:26.000Z","msg":"希望佢地唔好影完之後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己send黎send去笑</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:41:26.000Z","msg":"所以對果啲人係唔需要同情心"},{"pid":"a9b4265a9125807c9743ae91f3955fde64ca11c8","tid":1229101,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:41:26.000Z","msg":"巴打點解會行到呢一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c1ae90c0fb15811f8b7b13d11cb1e8baf8e574","tid":1229101,"uid":261396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1fa719526997e978e9dfaa6a6291aa43bc3050","tid":1229101,"uid":11695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:48:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀？ 遺書都收撚埋？"},{"pid":"ba0a2ee4d65f674ecfbdef4bdc9749e9a2007213",