5e6aff4c61e184bf84fa1ed70e24e1e800d6e","tid":1229101,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f1a59e71703c6bff5bae1d59b9c85a2b6ca8ae3","tid":1229101,"uid":260793,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:36:41.000Z","msg":"事主留下兩封遺書<br />\n據悉，死者姓梁(35歲)，家中有父母及姊妹，獨自前來，家人知悉後前往醫院了解，得知親人過世，家人傷心不已。據悉事主留下兩封遺書，其中一封講述家人如何為他辦理身後事，另一封遺書內容主要涉及不滿政府的修訂《逃犯條例》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=103723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Ffi%3Dnews1%26id%3D103723&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=5347f8d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=103723</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db4375e269887e852b97f5a2637ae7df3234787","tid":1229101,"uid":157474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b44f2c02d5bc53054990c496a047b835bda1eb3","tid":1229101,"uid":228464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T21:16:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收左去邊度？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】 一名身穿寫有抗議字句雨衣的男子，昨午危站金鐘太古廣場4樓平台邊緣，旁邊掛有一幅寫有「反送中」字句橫額。4個多小時後，男子爬出圍欄，消防抓着其上衣欲將他拉回安全位置時，男子掙扎，結果上衣甩脫，他飛墮而下，跌在救生氣墊旁地上，送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n太古廣場平台拉橫額<br />\n死者姓梁，35歲，<del><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">警方</span></span></del>稱<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在現場檢獲遺書</span></span>，暫未知遺書內容是否與反修例有關。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨午宣布暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》後，昨午4時許，太古廣場正圍封做工程的4樓平台外牆工作台，掛起一幅寫上「反送中」及「全面撤回送中，我們不是暴動，釋放學生傷者，林鄭下台」等字句的橫額，穿黃色雨衣的男子手持鎅刀站在橫額旁，背對金鐘道，雨衣上寫有「林鄭殺港，黑警冷血」等字眼。消防於金鐘道車路路面張開救生氣墊，警方亦到場調查，金鐘道西行兩線一度封閉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:15:26.000Z","msg":"你班警犬係咪寫左封比佢都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0246771a2e543a9d50c6b6f506a5ebdeec40f29","tid":1229101,"uid":21322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:19:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4eed80288bcd87c6502370c4eb91806c08dace7e","tid":1229101,"uid":22574,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:21:00.000Z","msg":"拎返都要對筆跡"},{"pid":"c8266c6428e40897f9c91ecf133b00188cf9266e","tid":1229101,"uid":228464,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"4eed80288bcd87c6502370c4eb91806c08dace7e","tid":1229101,"uid":22574,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:21:00.000Z","msg":"拎返都要對筆跡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:27:15.000Z","msg":"點解要搞到真係無曬信任...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96dace3576d724225bdc8da174cf801eba106834","tid":1229101,"uid":22574,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c8266c6428e40897f9c91ecf133b00188cf9266e","tid":1229101,"uid":228464,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"4eed80288bcd87c6502370c4eb91806c08dace7e","tid":1229101,"uid":22574,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:21:00.000Z","msg":"拎返都要對筆跡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:27:15.000Z","msg":"點解要搞到真係無曬信任...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:28:05.000Z","msg":"佢地有咩做唔出？"},{"pid":"7807c63b80d04b799756d3e3160a4f9cb1cf60c5","tid":1229101,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:30:45.000Z","msg":"終點禮賓府ok?"},{"pid":"4461401aeab135592cf47ac6d4d6ffab490d808c","tid":1229101,"uid":259321,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:34:50.000Z","msg":"陳雲：香港人，寧死不屈。共產黨，收